"Shadow Man" was the song I used when I made my first remix back in 2011. Now, four years later, I decided to remix it again, and this time it actually sounds good, or at least better.
For this remix, I only used 4 instruments: Acoustic piano (lead instrument), e-piano (comping), upright bass, and drums.
